# Engineering Standards — EGX Pro
# AI-Enforced Rules — All Generated Code Must Follow These Standards

---

## Tech Stack (Reference)

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4, Vite 6 |
| State | Zustand 5 |
| Forms | react-hook-form + Zod |
| Routing | react-router-dom v7 |
| UI Animation | Framer Motion |
| Charts | Recharts (dashboard) + Lightweight Charts (stock prices) |
| i18n | i18next + react-i18next |
| HTTP Client | Axios + axios-retry |
| Backend | Express 4, TypeScript |
| ORM | Prisma 6 + PostgreSQL |
| Cache | Upstash Redis |
| Auth | JWT (RS256) + HttpOnly Cookies |
| Logging | Winston |
| Monitoring | Sentry |
| WebSocket | ws |
| Email | Resend |
| Testing | Vitest + React Testing Library |
