## 12. Design System — Component Inventory

Use these components. Do not create alternatives.

| Component | Import | Use For |
|---|---|---|
| `<Button>` | `@/components/shared/Button` | All clickable actions |
| `<Input>` | `@/components/shared/Input` | All text inputs |
| `<EmptyState>` | `@/components/shared/EmptyState` | Empty lists |
| `<PageLoader>` | `@/components/shared/PageLoader` | Lazy load fallback |
| `<ErrorBoundary>` | `@/components/shared/ErrorBoundary` | Wrap all routes |
| `<SkeletonList>` | `@/components/shared/Skeleton` | Loading states |
| `<SettingsLayout>` | `@/components/layout/SettingsLayout` | Settings pages |
| `<BottomNav>` | `@/components/layout/BottomNav` | Mobile navigation |

