## 14. Git and CI/CD Rules

- `main` → Production only. Never push directly.
- `develop` → Staging. All features merge here first.
- `feature/xxx` → Individual features.

Every push to `main` or `develop` must pass:
1. `npx tsc --noEmit` — zero TypeScript errors
2. `npm run test` — all tests pass
3. `npm run build` — build succeeds
4. `npm audit --audit-level=high` — no high vulnerabilities

