## 15. Quick Reference Checklist

Before submitting any code, verify:

```
[ ] No file exceeds its line limit
[ ] No hardcoded colors (use CSS variables)
[ ] No magic numbers (use constants.ts)
[ ] No raw <button> or <input> (use Button/Input components)
[ ] No console.* in server code (use logger)
[ ] No console.log in frontend (use import.meta.env.DEV guard)
[ ] Every useEffect with fetch has AbortController cleanup
[ ] Every addEventListener has removeEventListener cleanup
[ ] Every setTimeout has clearTimeout cleanup
[ ] Every protected route has authenticate middleware
[ ] Every resource query checks userId ownership
[ ] Every form uses react-hook-form + Zod
[ ] Every list has loading/error/empty state handling
[ ] Every user-facing text uses t() from i18next
[ ] Every new Prisma model has @@index([userId])
[ ] TypeScript: zero errors (npx tsc --noEmit)
[ ] No non-null assertions (!.) without a guard above
[ ] No prop drilling beyond 1 level
```